closest to the river of the PNC Park offerings, Slice on Broadway is a sure bet! Fresh hand tossed pizza and related delicacies - garlic knots, bruschetta, focaccia and the like - with fresh pesto, tomato, or white sauce! Tasty ranch too! Wide selection of beers wines and liquors, Coca Cola products and lemonade! Definitely order up a pie for pickup or drop in for a drink, sure to please your palate!!